        "setup": "In [Salesloft Account](https://accounts.salesloft.com/oauth/applications), go to **Your Applications → API Keys → Create New**. Enter a name, choose at least one scope, save, and copy the generated key. Salesloft says API keys are for customers and are sent as `Authorization: Bearer YOUR_API_KEY`.",
