        "setup": "In [Salesloft Account](https://accounts.salesloft.com/oauth/applications), go to **Your Applications → OAuth Applications → Create New**. Create a private app with grant type **Client Credentials**, choose scopes, then exchange the app's client ID and client secret for an access token at `https://accounts.salesloft.com/oauth/token` using the `client_credentials` grant. The docs note this flow is admin-enabled for private application use only and assumes the permissions of the admin who created the app.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
